    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">菜名：</strong>猕猴桃香蕉拌酸奶 </p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">月龄：</strong>10m+</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">食材：</strong>猕猴桃、香蕉、酸奶</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/b3172195e67aa7285568d7f81a28b40d.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
