    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2.猕猴桃切片，香蕉切片；</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/30ca3ccad6201dd121a2fae5c27db0c0.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">3.拌入酸奶即可；</p>
